description:
I'm from the Philippines and a resident of the Philippines. I often go to Vegas to visit family.

I WOULD BE IN VEGAS THIS APRIL.

I'm a graduate of a medical course but ended up in the field of education.

I belong to a big family but we are all independent from each other.

I love pets since I used to have one when I was a kid. It is just that I was broken hearted when I lost him (Champ). 

I developed a new hobby since the pandemic and that is "plants". So, I am into it when I have the time. 

I'm more of a homebody person. I go out once in a while with friends. 

I'm looking for someone who would complement with me as I complement with him. I am a devout Christian and it is important to me to have someone who shares my faith. I'm more of the conservative type so I am easily taken aback with aggressive personality. 

On the weekends, I'm usually at home. (I also work from home) Unless there are some gatherings or meetings to attend.

Movies that I like are Shawshank Redemption, Primal Fear, or I can also be Mushy like Sweet November, The Notebook and be childish and nostalgic with Disney and Pixar Movies. 

I love listening to music that is why there is always music in my house playing, unless of course I'm working or sleeping. 

My friends are asking why I am not married. I also don't know. I believe I haven't met the one for me yet.
